# Vercel Deployment Ignore File
# Prevents large non-essential files from exceeding the 500MB Lambda limit.

# --- Large Documents ---
howacarworks.pdf
*.pdf

# --- Legacy & Scratch ---
_legacy_scripts/
scratch/
.tmp/
temp/
tests/
*.log

# --- Development Environment ---
.venv/
venv/
node_modules/
.git/
.gitignore
.vercelignore
README.md
ROADMAP.md
AGENTS.md
GEMINI.md
CLAUDE.md

# --- Database & Backups ---
*.db-journal
backups/
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# --- Media Source Files ---
# (Uncomment if you have large RAW videos in root)
# *.mp4
# *.mov
